					<td width="180" valign="top"><h2>VOLUNTARY ARDA ROC PAC CONTRIBUTION</h2>
						<p>The ARDA Resort Owners Coalition PAC is a non-profit political action comittee 
							sponsored by the American Resort Development Association, dedicated to 
							preserving, protecting and enhancing the ownership of vacation resort property.
							<BR>
							<BR>
							As a timeshare owner, your participation in ARDA ROC PAC aids in the American 
							Resort Development Association's legislative efforts on your behalf. Your 
							voluntary contributions are used to protect owners, like yourself, from 
							federal, state and local government attempts to raise revenue at the expense of 
							timeshare owners. For example, ARDA ROC PAC has been successful from protecting 
							owners from:
							<BR>
							<BR>
							<UL>
								<LI>
								Attempts to limit or eliminate the second home mortgage/timeshare deduction
								<LI>
								Attempts to impose state sales taxes on timeshares
								<LI>
									Attempts to tax owners of timeshares as transient occupants (i.e. hotel guests)</LI></UL>
							ARDA ROC PAC utilizes its contributions to hire consultants and experts to work 
							with ARDA Staff to track and follow legislative and regulatory activity in the 
							White House, regulatory agencies, the U.S. Congress and on the state and local 
							levels.
							<BR>
							<BR>
							Please join your fellow owners by contributing only $5.00 a year. Your support 
							will enable ARDA ROC PAC to protect your interests as a vacation resort owner. 
							For more information, go to <A href="http://www.arda.org" target="_blank" class="textlink">
								www.arda.org</A>. 
